<subSubSection id="4AF47AE50415758203ED7A8B72E2425B" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="description">
<paragraph id="FD0F72670023495EBA63776F7E3222C2" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4B2416A1748B3A7D1AE0D8DC74C1001E" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Colonies on PDA reaching 51 mm after 14 days at 25 °C, irregular in shape, cottony with moderately dense, fluffy aerial mycelium. At first, white, becoming slightly greyish in the centre, reverse side bronze in the centre and pale towards the edge.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
